  <brief_title>Flutamide In the Prevention of Prostate Cancer in Patients With Neoplasia of the Prostate</brief_title>
  <official_title>Short-Term Chemoprevention Trial in Men With Prostatic Intraepithelial Neoplasia Using Flutamide as an Androgen Deprivation Agent</official_title>
